data.description: Original masonry new construction duplex with additional 2 bedroom apartment as potential rental. Completely separate entrances to each of the units. All new foundation underpinning, drain tile, mechanical, electrical, and spray foam insulation. All the finishes speak for themselves as a modern inside of a solid brick A-Frame. Have you seen fortress walls this thick?All stainless steel appliances, high efficiency A/C and heating systems, 3 1/4 gray oak floors/ Malibu Wide Plank French maple flooring.  Property is nearing full completion. Please excuse any mess when showing the property as we are closing permits.
